        "created_at": "2020-02-06T23:01:45.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=3304715\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>2017 Comtesse Bernard de Cherisey Meursault-Blagny 1er Cru La Genelotte</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Beaune, Meursault-Blagny 1er Cru (1/31/2020)</em><br>\nAbsolutely brilliant. Vibrant fruit. Great volume. Very mineral finish. Both rich and racy. I love it.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
