        "created_at": "2020-02-07T14:58:45.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>It is located above and to the north of the hamlet of Blagny, and you can see it on this map: <a href=\"https://www.bourgogne-wines.com/our-wines-our-terroir/the-bourgogne-winegrowing-region-and-its-appellations/the-bourgogne-winegrowing-region-an-ideal-location,2458,9253.html?&amp;args=Y29tcF9pZD0yMjc4JmFjdGlvbj12aWV3SW1hZ2UmaWQ9Z2FsbGVyeV9pbWFnZXMlMkZzaXRlJTJGMyUyRjE5OTg4JTJGMTk5ODklMkYyMDAxOS5qcGcmfA%3D%3D&amp;view=image_copyright\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">The Bourgogne winegrowing region: an ideal and central location - Bourgogne wines</a></p>\n<p>It\u2019s spelt La Jeunelotte here, even though, since it\u2019s a monopole and Laurent Martelet spells it Genelotte, that\u2019s the only spelling you\u2019ll see on a label.</p>",
